ations are that early, widespread heating is favored over an extended\nperiod of heating that is associated with galaxy formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2005 10:53:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 29 Sep 2005 12:13:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 May 2006 16:51:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
